undations thereof fastened? or who laid the corner stone thereof;","year":-1520},{"id":"rec06hbt9pNZ7vsoL","ref":"Job.38.7","text":"When the morning stars sang together, and all the sons of God shouted for joy?","year":-1520},{"id":"rechMEpVt7RHKfdlJ","ref":"Job.38.8","text":"Or who shut up the sea with doors, when it brake forth, as if it had issued out of the womb?","year":-1520}]}
